      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i could call someone but i just don't see how talking helps. it's not like it brings him back. everything feels so pointless. i'm just so tired of waking up every morning and having to realize all over again that he's gone. the pain is just constant and it feels like it's never gonna stop.",
