      "content": "it just feels like i'm stuck in this loop of misery. like, why should i keep pushing through every day just to feel this emptiness? it feels like there's no actual way to make the pain stop, just a way to distract myself until i go to sleep. i just want the weight to be gone. i just want it to be quiet.",
